_______________________________________________________________________________
"Timeshift"        
        This power allows the psionicist to slow down the flow of time
        around him. Lasting a few combat rounds, it allows the psionicist
        to make more melee swings then normal, and helps them dodge
        incoming melee attacks a little better. A psionicist may not
        have more then one timeshift running for himself at any one time
        due to the complexities of manipulating the speed of time itself.
       
SP Cost:  Variable      Guild Level:  12        Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  timeshift
